plot: The second hour of a two-hour episode, Molly tries to reconcile whether she wants to be loyal to the aliens or remain loyal to the humans. JD becomes skeptical of the aliens after one gives him a flashback to his days in combat.

Lucy becomrs upset after discovering John Woods planned on making the Humanichs far more human attributes than she thought. In response, she acts out. JD becomes distrustful of the aliens. Molly must decide whether she wants to fight the aliens or support them.
